nhc_headline: ...AIR FORCE HURRICANE HUNTERS CURRENTLY INVSTIGATING HUMBERTO... ...DANGEROUS SURF WILL AFFECT BERMUDA AND MOST OF THE U.S. EAST COAST THIS WEEK...
summary: ...AIR FORCE HURRICANE HUNTERS CURRENTLY INVSTIGATING HUMBERTO... ...DANGEROUS SURF WILL AFFECT BERMUDA AND MOST OF THE U.S. EAST COAST THIS WEEK... As of 8:00 PM AST Sun Sep 28 the center of Humberto was located near 25.8, -65.7 with movement NW at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 928 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 145 mph.
